But actually, Singularity
University is not a university.

00:04:30.270 --> 00:04:31.770
And it is not about
the singularity.

00:04:32.890 --> 00:04:35.220
So the name is
kind of interesting

00:04:35.220 --> 00:04:38.360
because it really is about
a exponential technologies

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:41.130
to improve the
conditions of the world.

00:04:41.130 --> 00:04:44.480
I am myself from the
developing world.

00:04:44.480 --> 00:04:46.500
I grew up in Latin America.

00:04:46.500 --> 00:04:49.440
So I have experienced
what poverty is

00:04:49.440 --> 00:04:51.840
and how things can
change quickly.

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:54.280
So we are very happy
that among the founders

00:04:54.280 --> 00:04:57.830
effectively is Larry Page.

00:04:57.830 --> 00:05:00.430
But anyway, we have
many other companies

00:05:00.430 --> 00:05:02.430
supporting Singularity
University.

00:05:02.430 --> 00:05:06.600
The summer program basically
is structured in three parts.

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:09.460
The first part,
the participants--

00:05:09.460 --> 00:05:10.950
we don't call them
the students--

00:05:10.950 --> 00:05:13.900
the participants learn
about the technologies.

00:05:13.900 --> 00:05:17.540
In the second part, we have
convergence and site visits.

00:05:17.540 --> 00:05:20.880
And then the participants
begin working on film projects,

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:23.560
about how to use these
new technologies,

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:27.620
exponential technologies, to
improve the human condition.

00:05:27.620 --> 00:05:33.830
How to improve health, energy,
security, water, environment,

00:05:33.830 --> 00:05:37.450
all the problems of humanity
in the next few years.

00:05:37.450 --> 00:05:40.330
In fact, the goal is that the
students, or participants,

00:05:40.330 --> 00:05:44.150
have to finish with a project
to impact the world positively

00:05:44.150 --> 00:05:47.730
in 10 years, at least
for 1 billion people.

00:05:47.730 --> 00:05:50.750
So it is a big challenge, 1
billion people in 10 years.

00:05:52.140 --> 00:05:54.770
Some of the start-ups
that have originated out

00:05:54.770 --> 00:05:57.110
of Singularity University
are incredible companies

00:05:57.110 --> 00:06:00.410
like-- actually, I just
want to name Made in Space,

00:06:00.410 --> 00:06:04.840
because tomorrow history will be
written, and not just on Earth,

00:06:04.840 --> 00:06:05.840
in space.

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:09.980
Made in Space is taking
3D printers tomorrow

00:06:09.980 --> 00:06:12.240
to the International
Space Station.

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:14.950
This is the first
time humans will

00:06:14.950 --> 00:06:18.050
print something outside
of our tiny planet.

00:06:18.050 --> 00:06:20.520
This is the beginning
of colonization

00:06:20.520 --> 00:06:22.880
of the world, the
universe, and beyond.

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:25.530
And it is done by Singularity
University students.

00:06:25.530 --> 00:06:26.897
So we are really, really proud.

