The worst one is to be
passive, like an ostrich, that

00:17:49.080 --> 00:17:52.330
hides its head, doesn't want to
know what is going to happen.

00:17:52.330 --> 00:17:56.310
The second way is
to be reactive, OK,

00:17:56.310 --> 00:17:58.720
like a firefighter when
there is a problem.

00:17:58.720 --> 00:18:00.790
The third way is
to be preactive.

00:18:01.940 --> 00:18:03.480
When you buy
insurance, for example,

00:18:03.480 --> 00:18:04.900
to be prepared for something.

00:18:04.900 --> 00:18:07.390
But the best way
is to be proactive,

00:18:07.390 --> 00:18:09.260
to create the future
that you want,

00:18:09.260 --> 00:18:11.160
to build the future
that you want.

00:18:11.160 --> 00:18:14.320
So I hope that you
are proactive here

00:18:14.320 --> 00:18:16.140
and that there are
