00:21:06.980 --> 00:21:09.710
The Methuselah Foundation has
tried for the last 10 years

00:21:09.710 --> 00:21:12.849
to try to extend the
longevity of mice.

00:21:12.849 --> 00:21:14.390
And it's very
important and very easy

00:21:14.390 --> 00:21:16.320
to do experiments with
mice because they only

00:21:16.320 --> 00:21:17.700
live 1 year and 1/2.

00:21:17.700 --> 00:21:20.640
You cannot do experiments
with humans because we die

00:21:20.640 --> 00:21:21.840
in the middle of the road.

00:21:21.840 --> 00:21:23.540
But with a little
mouse that only

00:21:23.540 --> 00:21:25.920
lasts for a year and a half,
we can extend their lives

00:21:25.920 --> 00:21:27.280
and see the results.

00:21:27.280 --> 00:21:29.130
As of now, we have
some mice that

00:21:29.130 --> 00:21:31.990
