expected lifetime.

00:21:31.990 --> 00:21:35.520
That is mice that live
4 and 1/2 and 5 years.

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:39.060
We have Drosophila
melanogaster, the fruit

00:21:39.060 --> 00:21:41.920
