their regular lifespans.

00:21:41.920 --> 00:21:44.620
We have some worms
that actually live

00:21:44.620 --> 00:21:47.440
six times their normal lifespan.

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:48.520
And this isn't crazy.

00:21:48.520 --> 00:21:50.360
This has been done
in the last 10 years.

00:21:50.360 --> 00:21:53.640
So imagine what we are going
to do in the next 10 years?

