And I want to show you the
last 15 years of Asimo.

00:44:29.280 --> 00:44:32.430
Look what Honda has done
in the last 15 years.

00:44:32.430 --> 00:44:35.260
I ask you, can you
imagine what Honda

00:44:35.260 --> 00:44:36.960
will do in the next 15 years?

00:44:38.000 --> 00:44:43.910
They say that in 20 years,
they will win the World Cup.

00:44:43.910 --> 00:44:46.130
It will be a robot team
winning the World Cup.

00:44:47.170 --> 00:44:50.460
And robots will be fantastic,
with many degrees of motion,

00:44:50.460 --> 00:44:51.925
that we don't have, humans.

00:44:52.950 --> 00:44:55.220
And they will have feelings.

00:44:55.220 --> 00:44:57.585
At MIT, in the MIT
Media Lab, they

00:44:57.585 --> 00:45:02.820
are working on understanding
the feelings of robots.

00:45:02.820 --> 00:45:06.130
And in South Korea, they
are working on a law

00:45:06.130 --> 00:45:09.580
to give human rights to robots.

00:45:09.580 --> 00:45:12.740
You heard it was human
rights to robots.

00:45:12.740 --> 00:45:16.270
Because they believe
that in 10 to 15 years,

00:45:16.270 --> 00:45:18.680
every human will have a robot.

00:45:18.680 --> 00:45:20.245
And those robots
will not be stupid.

00:45:22.040 --> 00:45:24.410
And robots will be
absolutely fantastic.

00:45:24.410 --> 00:45:25.450
Imagine those robots.

00:45:26.840 --> 00:45:29.070
And also for the
women, don't desperate.

00:45:29.070 --> 00:45:32.520
You will have your
fantastic match of robots,

00:45:32.520 --> 00:45:35.360
with the additional advantage
that they will never

00:45:35.360 --> 00:45:36.610
get tired at night.

00:45:38.390 --> 00:45:42.890
Unfortunately, we think
normally that robots are bad.

00:45:42.890 --> 00:45:45.631
And that's because of the
former governor of California.

00:45:45.631 --> 00:45:46.513
[LAUGHTER]

00:45:47.840 --> 00:45:50.770
Who actually gave one
of the opening speeches

00:45:50.770 --> 00:45:54.860
at the inauguration of
Singularity University in 2009.

00:45:54.860 --> 00:45:59.060
And he said, fantastic that
you think about the future

00:45:59.060 --> 00:46:01.890
because the science
fiction of today

00:46:01.890 --> 00:46:03.620
is the science
reality of tomorrow.

00:46:04.700 --> 00:46:09.120
But here, because of Hollywood,
we think robots are bad.

00:46:09.120 --> 00:46:12.130
Even female robots are bad too.

00:46:13.350 --> 00:46:16.675
Including, when they
have sex, they are bad.

00:46:18.230 --> 00:46:22.000
But are robots good
or are robots bad?

00:46:22.000 --> 00:46:24.710
And I could tell you it
depends where you're from.

00:46:24.710 --> 00:46:26.530
It depends on your culture.

00:46:26.530 --> 00:46:30.290
If you grow up in
Japan, robots are good.

00:46:30.290 --> 00:46:33.760
In fact, robots are
better than humans.

00:46:33.760 --> 00:46:37.590
When a human has a
problem, they expect

00:46:37.590 --> 00:46:39.730
that a robot will help them.

00:46:39.730 --> 00:46:43.330
And there are many books
now in Japan-- for example,

00:46:43.330 --> 00:46:44.655
how to have sex with robots.

00:46:45.960 --> 00:46:47.290
And I'm not joking.

00:46:47.290 --> 00:46:50.320
The mentality of the Japanese,
and the Korean, and the Chinese

00:46:50.320 --> 00:46:51.560
is totally different.

00:46:51.560 --> 00:46:53.100
I will give you an
example that you

00:46:53.100 --> 00:46:55.030
will understand, with dragons.

00:46:56.050 --> 00:46:58.830
Dragons in China are good.

00:46:58.830 --> 00:47:00.910
Dragons in Korea
and Japan are good.

00:47:00.910 --> 00:47:03.260
But dragons in Europe are bad.

00:47:03.260 --> 00:47:04.970
European dragons are bad.

00:47:04.970 --> 00:47:06.210
They kill people.

00:47:06.210 --> 00:47:07.520
They destroy cities.

00:47:07.520 --> 00:47:09.110
They throw fire.

00:47:09.110 --> 00:47:11.120
But in Asia, they are good.

00:47:11.120 --> 00:47:12.410
The same with robots.

00:47:12.410 --> 00:47:14.320
Robots in Asia are good.

00:47:14.320 --> 00:47:16.200
And that is why
Japan and Korea are

00:47:16.200 --> 00:47:20.250
the leaders in humanoid
robotics in the world today.

00:47:20.250 --> 00:47:21.260
Because they are good.

00:47:21.260 --> 00:47:23.810
And all companies in
Japan are doing robots.

00:47:23.810 --> 00:47:26.730
At Honda, Toyota,
Fuji, all of them.

00:47:26.730 --> 00:47:30.000
But again, this is
not human or robot.

00:47:30.000 --> 00:47:32.370
This is human and machines.

00:47:32.370 --> 00:47:37.080
This is the synergy, the fusion,
of humans and our creations.

00:47:37.080 --> 00:47:40.260
We already saw that
in the London Olympics

00:47:40.260 --> 00:47:41.350
with Blade Runner.

00:47:42.740 --> 00:47:46.530
We saw this also at the
opening of the World Cup,

00:47:46.530 --> 00:47:50.150
where a paraplegic person,
connected to an exoskeleton

00:47:50.150 --> 00:47:53.600
with a device like this,
much more sophisticated,

00:47:53.600 --> 00:47:57.930
stood up and gave the initial
kickoff of the World Cup

00:47:57.930 --> 00:47:59.260
in Brazil.

00:47:59.260 --> 00:48:01.730
We are going to see
more in two years.

00:48:01.730 --> 00:48:03.470
After the Olympic
games in Brazil,

00:48:03.470 --> 00:48:09.220
there will be the first cyborg
Olympics in Zurich, Switzerland

00:48:09.220 --> 00:48:15.510
for discapacitated people, with
no legs, with no eyes, enhanced

00:48:15.510 --> 00:48:17.010
thanks to technology.

00:48:17.010 --> 00:48:19.450
This is coming in
two years in Zurich.

00:48:19.450 --> 00:48:21.270
This is the beginning
of these technologies

00:48:21.270 --> 00:48:22.780
used to enhance humans.

00:48:24.740 --> 00:48:27.710
All of this is
called transhumanism,

00:48:27.710 --> 00:48:31.000
which is transcending
human limitations thanks

00:48:31.000 --> 00:48:33.000
to science and technology.

00:48:33.000 --> 00:48:35.645
We humans, we are not
the end of evolution.

00:48:37.000 --> 00:48:40.260
We are just the beginning
of conscious evolution.

00:48:41.420 --> 00:48:46.410
Just like we are trans-monkeys,
there will be transhumans.

00:48:46.410 --> 00:48:48.800
But we have to do
this carefully.

00:48:48.800 --> 00:48:51.052
Because we don't want
to finish like that.

00:48:51.052 --> 00:48:52.290
[LAUGHTER]

00:48:52.290 --> 00:48:55.410
Our species is called
Homo sapiens sapiens,

00:48:55.410 --> 00:48:56.580
which is quite unique.

00:48:56.580 --> 00:49:00.540
This means the human
that knows, that knows.

00:49:00.540 --> 00:49:05.630
We are the first species that
is fully aware of its existence,

00:49:05.630 --> 00:49:07.000
as far as we know.

00:49:07.000 --> 00:49:08.050
But we are not the end.

00:49:08.050 --> 00:49:09.695
We are just the
beginning of this path.

00:49:11.000 --> 00:49:14.690
Life on this planet has
existed for about 3 and 1/2

00:49:14.690 --> 00:49:15.750
billion years.

00:49:15.750 --> 00:49:18.540
But the first 3 billion
years was only bacteria.

00:49:19.870 --> 00:49:23.240
Let me remind you,
bacteria are immortal.

00:49:23.240 --> 00:49:26.630
Or better, bacteria do not age.

00:49:26.630 --> 00:49:28.180
Also they have
round chromosomes.

00:49:28.180 --> 00:49:31.260
They have no telomeres because
they are completely round.

00:49:31.260 --> 00:49:33.360
So a bacteria does not age.

00:49:33.360 --> 00:49:35.200
It can die, if you kill it.

00:49:35.200 --> 00:49:36.690
But it does not age.

00:49:36.690 --> 00:49:41.174
Life appeared to be
alive, not to die.

00:49:41.174 --> 00:49:42.840
And that is the
beginning with bacteria.

00:49:42.840 --> 00:49:44.360
Anyway, humans we are very new.

00:49:44.360 --> 00:49:46.480
Humans, in our
current shape, we have

00:49:46.480 --> 00:49:49.440
existed for maybe 100,000 years.

00:49:49.440 --> 00:49:51.280
But we are not the
end of evolution.

00:49:51.280 --> 00:49:53.037
We are changing biologically.

00:49:53.037 --> 00:49:54.745
And now, we are changing
technologically.

00:49:56.830 --> 00:50:00.310
In the next few years, we are
going to cure all diseases.

00:50:01.490 --> 00:50:03.760
There will be [INAUDIBLE]
paraplegics in 10 years.

00:50:03.760 --> 00:50:05.930
We will not have these
horrible diseases.

00:50:05.930 --> 00:50:07.062
No more Parkinson's.

00:50:07.062 --> 00:50:07.895
No more Alzheimer's.

00:50:09.010 --> 00:50:10.590
No more aging.

00:50:10.590 --> 00:50:15.920
We are going to see the death
of death in the next few years.

00:50:15.920 --> 00:50:20.310
But everything has ying and
yang, as the Chinese say.

